01:12:29.750 --> 01:12:30.750
Ko?

01:12:33.417 --> 01:12:34.458
Moj je.

01:12:40.792 --> 01:12:42.167
Pogledaj u drugi džep.

01:12:43.500 --> 01:12:44.500
