Izabela!

01:24:50.608 --> 01:24:51.942
Tražim tvoju rođaku, Terezu.

01:24:52.025 --> 01:24:53.025
Henri...
- Ulica Don Telo.

01:24:53.108 --> 01:24:54.775
Treba mi tvoja pomoć.
- Tamo!

01:24:54.817 --> 01:24:55.817
Ovuda?

01:25:00.483 --> 01:25:01.983
Ne!
- Ne. Ne, Izabela.

01:25:02.067 --> 01:25:03.108
Ne, ne možeš!

01:25:03.150 --> 01:25:05.275
Moja haljina! To
